@baseUrl = http://localhost:8082
@adminToken = replace-with-admin-access-token
@userToken = replace-with-normal-user-access-token

### 1. 查询低库存商品
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/assistant/chat
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "查询低库存商品"
}

### 2. 统计订单状态
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/assistant/chat
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "统计最近 7 天订单状态"
}

### 3. 普通用户访问，应返回 403 且不调用 LLM
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/assistant/chat
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "查询低库存商品"
}

### 4. 未登录访问，应返回 401
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/assistant/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "查询低库存商品"
}
